Subject: drm/amdgpu/gmc6: fix DMA mask from 44 to 40 bits
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: 403475be6d8b122c3e6b8a47e075926d7299e5ef
